最近读到的：
 In an image-centered and pleasure-driven world, there is no place for rational thinking, because you simply cannot think with images. It is text that enables us to &ldquo;uncover lies, confusions and overgeneralizations, and to detect abuses of logic and common sense. It also means to weigh ideas, to compare and contrast assertions, to connect one generalization to another.&rdquo;
 That&rsquo;s Why I love TeXT. 回到固有的生动活泼的思考。
